    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Morphs</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Morph abilities last for a brief period. Cannot die in morph state!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loss of all health will de-morph back to the base hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in fearless Kamikaze caliber battles using morph abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/64d81a4aad689b5064c38671908f0f30.poster.avif?t=1767763353\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/64d81a4aad689b5064c38671908f0f30.webm?t=1767763353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/64d81a4aad689b5064c38671908f0f30.mp4?t=1767763353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mounts</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse impassable terrains such as seas, skies and outer space using mounts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/05c2f0ca98e5685029cf0caa8e05d19f.poster.avif?t=1767763353\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/05c2f0ca98e5685029cf0caa8e05d19f.webm?t=1767763353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/05c2f0ca98e5685029cf0caa8e05d19f.mp4?t=1767763353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Summons</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon armies to fight your battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/275a30232b019ab8b7b7214b4c43a462.poster.avif?t=1767763353\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/275a30232b019ab8b7b7214b4c43a462.webm?t=1767763353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106150/extras/275a30232b019ab8b7b7214b4c43a462.mp4?t=1767763353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resources</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slay enemy races for meat and sea food.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather wood by chopping trees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
